title: BVS Video Poker 1.5.1FULL
description:
BVS Video Poker game combines video poker simulator with hand
analysis feature. It warns you when you make mistakes and shows
you the best play with the higest expected value for every hand.
It helps you to fine-tune your video poker playing skills. All
the most popular video poker machines are included: Jacks or
Better, Deuces Wild, Joker Poker, Loose Deuces, Deuces Joker and
more. Version 1.5.1 may include unspecified updates,
enhancements, or bug fixes.
